Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5)
Standards-Version: 3.7.3
Homepage: http://johan.kiviniemi.name/software/hardware-connected/

Package: hardware-connected
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, module-init-tools
Description: indicates whether given hardware exists in the system
 A module name or a list of modalias patterns is passed to this tool and its
 return code indicates whether the hardware is connected to the system.
